Subject: Attention Runtime Registry

Description: Semantic runtime registry for tracking active attention like inspectable stack frames over focus, periphery, Wisdom, Caution, and integration.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_attention_runtime_registry\Dictated_Attention_Runtime_Registry_Source.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\FocusResolutionRefinement.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\FocalPoint.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\FocusZoom.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\AttentionTraversalPolicy.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\Wisdom.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\Caution.sop
